#

Spicy Honey Garlic Chicken

30 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

AmericanAsian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickHealthy

Description

A sweet and spicy chicken dish that’s bursting with flavor and takes only 30 minutes to make!

Ingredients

  • chicken thighs (boneless): 1 lb
  • honey: 1/4 cup
  • soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • red pepper flakes: 1 tsp
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • green onions (chopped, for garnish): optional
